  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK345">
<l>maṟṟun toṭarppā ṭevaṉkol piṟappaṟukka</l>
<l>luṟṟārk kuṭampu mikai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What means the addition of other things those who are attempting to cut off (future) births, when even their body is too much (for them).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
